     :target: https://pyup.io/repos/github/biavillas/estela/

A python package based on the ESTELA method for evaluating the source and travel time of the wave energy reaching a local area , as proposed by Pérez et al. (2014).


* Free software: BSD license
* Documentation: https://estela.readthedocs.io.
